Class HashBidiMultiMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
net.sf.cotelab.util.collections.HashMultiMap<K,V>
net.sf.cotelab.util.collections.HashBidiMultiMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the type of key to be supported.
V - the type of value to be supported.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BidiMultiMap<K,V>, MultiMap<K,V>
public class HashBidiMultiMap<K,V> extends HashMultiMap<K,V> implements BidiMultiMap<K,V>, Serializable
An implementation of the BidiMultiMap interface, using hashed indexes.
Author:
alancote@rochester.rr.com
